  "body": "`franklin stop` runs in the local environment and tries to stop pg. Pg is run from docker compose in local dev environment.\n\nIt is sign of a problem in the current local dev setup.\nNow we have 1) local dev setup 2) local dev kube setup 3) digital ocean kube setup\n\n1 and 2 is in conflict rn\n\nI imagine good solution to have the following properties.\n\n1) local dev kube setup and do kube setup should be almost identical\nand deployment to 1 and another should be done with similar commands\n\nWe run pg and geth in minikube, so I imagine it makes local dev kube and do kube not identical.\n\n2) local dev setup should support iterative and fast local development (no docker images for running node, easy way to reset local network (rebuild redeploy contracts, reset db)\n\n(this is more or less true RN)\n\n\nI propose to change local dev setup with this two constraints in mind.",
